---
// AboutHero.astro
// Editorial-style Hero section for LUMÉ Jewelry About page
---

<section class="relative w-full pt-32 pb-16 md:pt-40 md:pb-24 px-4 md:px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center select-none">
  <!-- Subtle top accent -->
  <span class="text-[10px] md:text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#7C0A12] mb-3 animate-fade-in-down">
    Nuestra Historia
  </span>
  
  <!-- Headline -->
  <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl text-[#1C1917] text-center max-w-4xl tracking-tighter leading-[1.1] md:leading-[1.05]">
    Crear con intención,<br class="hidden sm:inline" />
    <span class="italic text-[#7C0A12] font-normal">llevar con propósito</span>.
  </h1>

  <!-- Divider line -->
  <div class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-[#78716C]/30 my-8 md:my-12"></div>

  <!-- Subheadline -->
  <p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl text-[#78716C] font-light text-center max-w-2xl leading-relaxed text-balance">
    LUMÉ nace bajo la dirección creativa de Nata, fusionando la fuerza de las piedras naturales y la elegancia de los metales nobles en piezas únicas diseñadas y hechas a mano en Bolivia.
  </p>

  <!-- Interactive scroll-down hint (visual only) -->
  <div class="mt-12 md:mt-16 animate-bounce">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-[#78716C]/60" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes fadeInDown {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(-8px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .animate-fade-in-down {
    animation: fadeInDown 800ms cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1) forwards;
  }
</style>
